          "hash": "adb9cd58654bfb2a66b51cb0ab0cd5214067cb2b7c4af06e4317531ee1f084b8"
        },
        {
          "text": "to say 'it is not'. How would you say 'it is not'?",
          "lang": "en",
          "file": "turn-30-full-7.mp3",
          "hash": "68ac754ad1cae065f8e777f7a183d30f24573f36f167dd69564fcb8871062c93"
        }
      ]
    },
    "turn-32-full": {
      "segments": [
        {
          "text": "No es.",
          "lang": "es",
          "file": "turn-32-full-1.mp3",
          "hash": "fe815ca33612a8bf645fd102ac3f1e1fc35b2cb884de52693d2128274f9e6a3d"
        },
        {
          "text": "Good. So now we can say things like 'it's not normal'.",
          "lang": "en",
